orks analysis. In the model\nindependent analysis, we also find evidence for a closed Universe, and the flat\nUniverse is almost 1$\\sigma$ away. So, both the model dependent and independent\nanalyses favor a closed Universe from the combinations of CC, QSO, and $H_0$\nobservations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2023 17:19:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Mar 2023 17:39:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
